Package environment

Class ToHandle

  • java.lang.Object
    • environment.ToHandle
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EOPSet, InfluenceSet, MailBag
    public abstract class ToHandle
extends java.lang.Object
    A generic class for facilitating communication between Spheres and Handlers. A ToHandle keeps e reference to the sending sphere, together with the number of outcomes that are dealt with when the ToHandle has been handled.
